Dedicate SQL PoolServerless SQL Pool <pre><code>CREATE EXTERNAL DATA SOURCE [&lt;external-data-source&gt;]
WITH(
    LOCATION = 'abfss://&lt;container&gt;@&lt;storage-account&gt;.dfs.core.windows.net',
    CREDENTIAL = &lt;credential-name&gt;,
    PUSHDOWN = ON,
    TYPE = HADOOP
);
</code></pre> <p>Note</p> <p>PolyBase data virtualization is used when the <code>EXTERNAL DATA SOURCE</code> is created with <code>TYPE=HADOOP</code>.</p> <p><code>PUSHDOWN = ON | OFF</code> is set to <code>ON</code> by default, meaning the ODBC Driver can leverage server-side processing for complex queries.</p> <pre><code>CREATE EXTERNAL DATA SOURCE [&lt;external-data-source&gt;]
